data.description: Welcome to this inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spanning a comfortable 1,689 square feet. Built in 2008, this home exudes a warm and welcoming atmosphere perfect for anyone seeking both comfort and practicality. Not only does this home offer modern amenities like refrigerated air but also includes a split floor plan as well as a low maintenance backyard. Located in close proximity to stores and restaurants, convenience is at your doorstep.
